cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with modeling human activities in videos, which involves computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a robotic system that applies the action patching algorithm, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper uses a probabilistic model to relate words and topics, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with video data, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
